---
import Schedule from "@/components/Schedule"

const {number} = Astro.props
---

<main
	class='w-full h-auto text-center mt-14 px-10 flex justify-center items-center'
>
	<div>
		<div>
			<h2 class='font-bold sm:text-[80px] text-5xl text-[#1a73e8] leading-[1]'>
				Aumente as vendas
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div class='relative z-20'>
			<p
				class='sm:text-[80px] text-5xl text-[#202124] font-bold leading-[1] tracking-[-2.5px]'
			>
				com Anúncios Online
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class='-mt-10'>
			<div
				class='relative flex justify-center items-center mx-auto w-80 h-80 bg-[#d2e3fc] [clip-path:circle(50%)] pb-10'
			>
				<div
					class="relative w-full h-full bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-[url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/T1huE9epB2KD3ECsJ58CePSwl2UN0Cpo_8EMbyy-4UTX1riw7Kwy90o-ou__mgxG6_Vueu9TJyqhg_4q7MWGWZHlBDv5e219Knkj9Gw2O-5TtdXfwGM=w230-rw-v1')]"
				>
				</div>
				<span
					class='absolute tracking-[0.3px] font-medium top-[243px] left-[84px] text-lg text-white'
				>
					Shopping
				</span>
				<span
					class='absolute text-[#4285f4] text-base tracking-[0.3px] font-medium top-[145px] left-[86px]'
				>
					Liquida calçados
				</span>
				<span class='absolute text-[#80868b] text-xs top-[175px] left-[86px]'>
					Confira as coleções
				</span>
				<span
					class='absolute text-[#80868b] text-[8px] top-[203px] left-[82px]'
				>
					exemplosdenegocios.com.br
				</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</main>

<section class='flex justify-center flex-col mt-14 md:mx-40'>
	<p class='text-[#3c4043] text-center text-xl px-10'>
		Para todas as necessidades, como gestor de tráfego, possibilito que seus
		potenciais clientes encontrem sua empresa com facilidade através dos anúncios.
	</p>

	<div class='flex justify-center items-center gap-4 mt-12'>
		<a
			href={number}
			target='_blank'
			class='h-full sm:text-base text-xs bg-[#1a73e8] border-[1px] rounded-[4px] min-w-24 min-h-12 max-w-96 tracking-[.5px] font-medium text-white py-3 px-7 sm:inline-flex hidden items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#185abc] focus:bg-[#185abc] focus:border-[2px]'
		>
			Entre em contato
		</a>
		<Schedule client:idle/>
	</div>
</section>
